        "text": "Yeah — I'm not looking for something _magic_. I'm happy with LWW (or whatever) at the level of individual leaf nodes within a big structure of CRDTs (or whatever). I just don't want to have to implement said CRDTs myself.\n\nIn other words — I'm happy to write the logic for \"What should happen when one element of this CRDT set has multiple divergent edits?\" as long as I don't have to write the logic for \"What should happen when two separate elements of this CRDT set have independent edits?\"",
