        "client_msg_id": "C86ED082-D029-4763-AE87-EF057D972E96",
        "text": "Regarding “I don’t want to have to implement CRDTs”, isn’t the logic really damn simple? That’s why the whole notion of “CRDT libraries” has always perplexed me: the simple resolution schemes are easy to implement manually, and the complex ones MUST be implemented manually because they aren’t going to be generic.",
